---
title: Medi Burgers and Olive Tapenade with Greek Salad
description: A DIY olive tapenade cascade down a juicy prime rib burger patty, while feta mayo and crisp baby spinach fill out the rest of the soft brioche bun. A veggie-packed Greek salad is the perfect pairing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/medi-burgers-and-olive-tapenade-bea71d8c.jpg
